{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So, 120 years ago,"},{"time":4000,"text":"Dr. RÃ¶ntgen X-rayed his wife's hand."},{"time":6000,"text":"Quite why he had to pin her fingers to the floor"},{"time":9000,"text":"with her brooch, I'm not sure. It seems a bit extreme to me."},{"time":12000,"text":"That image was the start of the X-ray technology."},{"time":15000,"text":"And I'm still fundamentally using the same principles today."},{"time":18000,"text":"I'm interpreting it in a more contemporary manner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22000,"text":"The first shot I ever did"},{"time":26000,"text":"was of a soda can, which was to promote a brand that we all know,"},{"time":29000,"text":"so I'm not going to do them any favors by showing you it."},{"time":31000,"text":"But the second shot I did was my shoes I was wearing on the day."},{"time":34000,"text":"And I do really like this shot, because"},{"time":36000,"text":"it shows all the detritus that's sort of embedded"},{"time":38000,"text":"in the sole of the sneakers."},{"time":40000,"text":"It was just one of those pot-luck things where you"},{"time":42000,"text":"get it right first time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44000,"text":"Moving on to something a bit larger,"},{"time":46000,"text":"this is an X-ray of a bus."},{"time":48000,"text":"And the bus is full of people."},{"time":50000,"text":"It's actually the same person. It's just one skeleton."},{"time":52000,"text":"And back in the '60s,"},{"time":54000,"text":"they used to teach student radiographers"},{"time":56000,"text":"to take X-rays, thankfully not on you and I,"},{"time":58000,"text":"but on dead people."},{"time":60000,"text":"So, I've still got access to one of these dead people"},{"time":62000,"text":"called Frieda; she's falling apart, I'm afraid,"},{"time":65000,"text":"because she's very old and fragile."},{"time":67000,"text":"But everyone on that bus is Frieda."},{"time":69000,"text":"And the bus is taken with a cargo-scanning X-ray,"},{"time":72000,"text":"which is the sort of machine you have on borders,"},{"time":74000,"text":"which checks for contraband and drugs and bombs and things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78000,"text":"Fairly obvious what that is."},{"time":81000,"text":"So, using large-scale objects"},{"time":83000,"text":"does sort of create drama"},{"time":85000,"text":"because you just don't see X-rays of big things that often."},{"time":88000,"text":"Technology is moving ahead,"},{"time":90000,"text":"and these large cargo scanner X-rays"},{"time":93000,"text":"that work with the digital system are getting better and better and better."},{"time":95000,"text":"Again though, to make it come alive"},{"time":97000,"text":"you need, somehow, to add the human element."},{"time":99000,"text":"And I think the reason this image works, again, is because"},{"time":101000,"text":"Frieda is driving the bulldozer."},{"time":103000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":104000,"text":"Quite a difficult brief,"},{"time":106000,"text":"make a pair of men's pants look beautiful."},{"time":108000,"text":"But I think the process, in itself, shows how exquisite they are."},{"time":113000,"text":"Fashion -- now, I'm sort of anti-fashion because I"},{"time":115000,"text":"don't show the surface, I show what's within."},{"time":117000,"text":"So, the fashionistas don't really like me"},{"time":119000,"text":"because it doesn't matter if Kate Moss is wearing it or if I'm wearing it,"},{"time":121000,"text":"it looks the same."},{"time":123000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":125000,"text":"We all look the same inside, believe me."},{"time":127000,"text":"The creases in the material and the sort of nuances."},{"time":131000,"text":"And I show things for really what they are, what they're made of."},{"time":133000,"text":"I peel back the layers and expose it."},{"time":136000,"text":"And if it's well made I show it, if it's badly made I show it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138000,"text":"And I'm sure Ross can associate that with design."},{"time":141000,"text":"The design comes from within."},{"time":143000,"text":"It's not just Topshop,"},{"time":145000,"text":"I get some strange looks when I go out getting my props."},{"time":147000,"text":"Here I was fumbling around in the ladies' underwear department"},{"time":149000,"text":"of a department store, almost got escorted from the premises."},{"time":153000,"text":"I live opposite a farm. And this was the runt of the litter, a piglet that died."},{"time":156000,"text":"And what's really interesting is,"},{"time":158000,"text":"if you look at the legs, you'll notice that the bones haven't fused."},{"time":161000,"text":"And should that pig have grown,"},{"time":163000,"text":"unfortunately it was dead, it would have certainly been dead"},{"time":165000,"text":"after I X-rayed it, with the amount of radiation I used anyway."},{"time":167000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":168000,"text":"But once the bones had fused together"},{"time":171000,"text":"it would have been healthy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173000,"text":"So, that's an empty parka jacket."},{"time":176000,"text":"But I quite love the way it's posed."},{"time":178000,"text":"Nature is my greatest inspiration."},{"time":180000,"text":"And to carry on with a theme that we've already touched with"},{"time":183000,"text":"is how nature is related to architecture."},{"time":186000,"text":"If you look at the roof of the Eden Project,"},{"time":189000,"text":"or the British library, it's all this honeycomb structure."},{"time":191000,"text":"And I'm sure those architects are inspired,"},{"time":193000,"text":"as I am, by what surrounds us, by nature."},{"time":196000,"text":"This, in fact, is a Victoria water lily leaf"},{"time":199000,"text":"that floats on the top of a pond."},{"time":201000,"text":"An amaryllis flower looking really three-dimensional."},{"time":205000,"text":"Seaweed, ebbing in the tide."},{"time":207000,"text":"Now, how do I do this, and where do I do this, and all of that sort of thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"This is my new, purpose-built, X-ray shed."},{"time":212000,"text":"And the door to my X-ray room"},{"time":216000,"text":"is made of lead and steel."},{"time":218000,"text":"It weighs 1,250 kilograms and the only exercise I get is opening and closing it."},{"time":222000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":225000,"text":"The walls are 700 millimeters thick of solid dense concrete."},{"time":228000,"text":"So, I'm using quite a lot of radiation."},{"time":230000,"text":"A lot more than you'd get in a hospital or a vet's."},{"time":233000,"text":"And there I am. This is a quite high-powered X-ray machine."},{"time":236000,"text":"What's interesting really about X-ray really"},{"time":239000,"text":"is, if you think about it, is that that technology"},{"time":241000,"text":"is used for looking for cancer or looking for drugs,"},{"time":243000,"text":"or looking for contraband or whatever."},{"time":245000,"text":"And I use that sort of technology"},{"time":247000,"text":"to create things that are quite beautiful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250000,"text":"So, still working with film, I'm afraid."},{"time":252000,"text":"Technology in X-ray where it's life-size processed,"},{"time":255000,"text":"apart from these large cargo-scanning machines,"},{"time":257000,"text":"hasn't moved on enough for the quality of the image"},{"time":260000,"text":"and the resolution to be good enough for what I want to do with it,"},{"time":262000,"text":"which is show my pictures big."},{"time":264000,"text":"So, I have to use a 1980s drum scanner,"},{"time":268000,"text":"which was designed in the days when everyone shot photographs on film."},{"time":271000,"text":"They scan each individual X-ray."},{"time":273000,"text":"And this shows how I do my process of same-size X-rays."},{"time":276000,"text":"So, this is, again, my daughter's dress."},{"time":278000,"text":"Still has the tag in it from me buying it,"},{"time":280000,"text":"so I can take it back to the shop if she didn't like it."},{"time":282000,"text":"But there are four X-ray plates."},{"time":284000,"text":"You can see them overlapping."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286000,"text":"So, when you move forward from something fairly small,"},{"time":289000,"text":"a dress which is this size,"},{"time":291000,"text":"onto something like that which is done in exactly the same process,"},{"time":294000,"text":"you can see that that is a lot of work."},{"time":296000,"text":"In fact, that is three months solid X-raying."},{"time":298000,"text":"There is over 500 separate components."},{"time":301000,"text":"Boeing sent me a 747 in containers."},{"time":303000,"text":"And I sent them back an X-ray."},{"time":305000,"text":"(Laughter) I kid you not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307000,"text":"Okay, so Frieda is my dead skeleton."},{"time":309000,"text":"This, unfortunately, is basically two pictures."},{"time":312000,"text":"One on the extreme right is a photograph of an American footballer."},{"time":315000,"text":"The one on the left is an x-ray."},{"time":317000,"text":"But this time I had to use a real body."},{"time":319000,"text":"Because I needed all the skin tissue to make it look real,"},{"time":321000,"text":"to make it look like it was a real athlete."},{"time":323000,"text":"So, here I had to use a recently deceased body."},{"time":325000,"text":"And getting a hold of that was extremely difficult and laborious."},{"time":330000,"text":"But people do donate their bodies to art and science."},{"time":332000,"text":"And when they do, I'm in the queue."},{"time":334000,"text":"So, I like to use them."},{"time":336000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":337000,"text":"The coloring, so coloring adds another level to the X-rays."},{"time":342000,"text":"It makes it more organic, more natural."},{"time":344000,"text":"It's whatever takes my fancy, really."},{"time":346000,"text":"It's not accurately colored to how it is in real life."},{"time":349000,"text":"That flower doesn't come in bright orange, I don't think."},{"time":351000,"text":"But I just like it in bright orange."},{"time":353000,"text":"And also with something technical, like these are DJ decks,"},{"time":355000,"text":"it sort of adds another level."},{"time":357000,"text":"It makes a two dimensional image look more three dimensional."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361000,"text":"The most difficult things to X-ray,"},{"time":363000,"text":"the most technically challenging things to X-ray"},{"time":365000,"text":"are the lightest things, the most delicate things."},{"time":367000,"text":"To get the detail in a feather,"},{"time":369000,"text":"believe me, if there is anyone out here who knows anything about X-rays,"},{"time":371000,"text":"that's quite a challenge."},{"time":373000,"text":"I'm now going to show you a short film, I'll step to the side."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378000,"text":"Video: (Music)"},{"time":397000,"text":"The thing in there is very dangerous."},{"time":399000,"text":"If you touch that, you could possibly die"},{"time":401000,"text":"through radiation poisoning."},{"time":403000,"text":"In my career I've had two exposures to radiation,"},{"time":405000,"text":"which is two too many, because it stays with you for life."},{"time":407000,"text":"It's cumulative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":418000,"text":"It has human connotations."},{"time":419000,"text":"The fact that it's a child's toy that we all recognize,"},{"time":422000,"text":"but also it looks like it's a robot,"},{"time":425000,"text":"and it comes from a sci-fi genus."},{"time":430000,"text":"It's a surprise that it has humanity,"},{"time":433000,"text":"but also man-made, future, alien associations."},{"time":441000,"text":"And it's just a bit spooky."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":478000,"text":"The bus was done with a cargo-scanning X-ray machine,"},{"time":481000,"text":"which is used on the borders"},{"time":483000,"text":"between countries, looking for contraband and illegal immigrants."},{"time":486000,"text":"The lorry goes in front of it. And it takes slices"},{"time":489000,"text":"of X-rays through the lorry."},{"time":491000,"text":"And that's how this was done. It's actually slice, slice."},{"time":493000,"text":"It's a bit like a CT scanner in a hospital. Slices."},{"time":495000,"text":"And then if you look carefully, there is all little things."},{"time":498000,"text":"He's got headphones on, reading the newspaper,"},{"time":500000,"text":"got a hat on, glasses, got a bag."},{"time":503000,"text":"So, these little details"},{"time":506000,"text":"help to make it work, make it real."}]},{"cues":[{"time":509000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":516000,"text":"The problem with using living people is that"},{"time":518000,"text":"to take an X-ray, if I X-ray you, you get exposed to radiation."},{"time":521000,"text":"So, to avoid that --"},{"time":523000,"text":"I have to avoid it somehow --"},{"time":525000,"text":"is I use dead people."},{"time":527000,"text":"Now, that's a variety of things, from recently deceased bodies,"},{"time":531000,"text":"to a skeleton that was used by student radiographers"},{"time":536000,"text":"to train in taking X-rays of the human body,"},{"time":539000,"text":"at different densities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":546000,"text":"I have very high-tech equipment of gloves, scissors and a bucket."}]},{"cues":[{"time":549000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":556000,"text":"I will show how the capillary action works, how it feeds,"},{"time":559000,"text":"I'll be able to get all the cells inside that stem."},{"time":561000,"text":"Because it transfers food from its roots to its leaves."},{"time":565000,"text":"Look at this monster."}]},{"cues":[{"time":567000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":579000,"text":"It's so basic. It just grows wild."},{"time":582000,"text":"That's what I really like about it,"},{"time":584000,"text":"the fact that I haven't got to go and buy it,"},{"time":586000,"text":"and it hasn't been genetically modified at all."},{"time":588000,"text":"It's just happening."},{"time":590000,"text":"And the X-ray shows how beautiful nature can be."},{"time":593000,"text":"Not that that is particularly beautiful"},{"time":595000,"text":"when you look at it with the human eye,"},{"time":598000,"text":"the way the leaves form. They're curling back on each other."},{"time":602000,"text":"So the X-ray will show the overlaps in these little corners."},{"time":616000,"text":"The thicker the object, the more radiation it needs,"},{"time":618000,"text":"and the more time it needs."},{"time":620000,"text":"The lighter the object, the less radiation."},{"time":623000,"text":"Sometimes you keep the time up, because the time gives you detail."},{"time":626000,"text":"The longer the exposure goes on for,"},{"time":628000,"text":"the more detail you get."}]},{"cues":[{"time":631000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":645000,"text":"If you look at this, just the tube,"},{"time":647000,"text":"it is quite bright."},{"time":649000,"text":"But I could get a bit darker in the tube, but everything else would suffer."},{"time":652000,"text":"So, these leaves at the edge would start to disappear."},{"time":656000,"text":"What I like is how hard the edges are,"},{"time":658000,"text":"how sharp."},{"time":660000,"text":"Yeah, I'm quite pleased with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":662000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":664000,"text":"I travel beyond the surface and show"},{"time":666000,"text":"something for what it's worth,"},{"time":669000,"text":"for what it's really made of, how it really works."},{"time":671000,"text":"But also I find that"},{"time":674000,"text":"I've got the benefit of taking away all the surface,"},{"time":678000,"text":"which is things that people are used to seeing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":682000,"text":"And that's the sort of thing I've been doing."},{"time":684000,"text":"I've got the opportunity now to show you"},{"time":686000,"text":"what I'm going to be doing in the future."},{"time":688000,"text":"This is a commercial application of my most recent work."},{"time":692000,"text":"And what's good about this, I think, is that it's like a moment in time,"},{"time":695000,"text":"like you've turned around, you've got X-ray vision"},{"time":697000,"text":"and you've taken a picture with the X-ray camera."},{"time":699000,"text":"Unfortunately I haven't got X-ray vision."},{"time":701000,"text":"I do dream in X-ray. I see my projects in my sleep."},{"time":704000,"text":"And I know what they're going to look like in X-ray and I'm not far off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":707000,"text":"So, what am I doing in the future?"},{"time":709000,"text":"Well, this year is the 50th anniversary"},{"time":711000,"text":"of Issigonis's Mini, which is one of my favorite cars."},{"time":714000,"text":"So, I've taken it apart, component by component,"},{"time":717000,"text":"months and months and months of work."},{"time":719000,"text":"And with this image, I'm going to be displaying"},{"time":722000,"text":"it in the Victoria and Albert Museum"},{"time":725000,"text":"as a light box, which is actually attached to the car."},{"time":727000,"text":"So, I've got to saw the car in half, down the middle,"},{"time":730000,"text":"not an easy task, in itself."},{"time":732000,"text":"And then, so you can get in the driver's side, sit down,"},{"time":734000,"text":"and up against you is a wall."},{"time":736000,"text":"And if you get out and walk around to the other side of the car,"},{"time":738000,"text":"you see a life-sized light box of the car showing you how it works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":741000,"text":"And I'm going to take that idea"},{"time":743000,"text":"and apply it to other sort of iconic things from my life."},{"time":747000,"text":"Like, my first computer was a big movement in my life."},{"time":750000,"text":"And I had a Mac Classic. And it's a little box."},{"time":752000,"text":"And I think that would look quite neat as an X-ray."},{"time":755000,"text":"I'm also looking to"},{"time":757000,"text":"take my work from the two-dimensional form"},{"time":759000,"text":"to a more three-dimensional form."},{"time":761000,"text":"And this is quite a good way of doing it."},{"time":764000,"text":"I'm also working now with X-ray video."},{"time":766000,"text":"So, if you can imagine, some of these flowers,"},{"time":768000,"text":"and they're actually moving and growing"},{"time":770000,"text":"and you can film that in X-ray, should be quite stunning."},{"time":773000,"text":"But that's it. I'm done. Thank you very much."},{"time":775000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}